The paper discusses the integration of OCR data with a relational database management system, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of probabilistic models and text indexing, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper mentions the OCR process for scanned documents and forms, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG).
